msgid ""
"Rule identifiers in the path are matched against `cprmv:id` literals in the "
"RDF graph using the following normalisation:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cuser-guide%5Crule-path-syntax.md:63
msgid ""
"All non-alphanumeric characters (spaces, periods, parentheses, hyphens, "
"slashes) are **stripped** from both the path segment and the stored "
"identifier before comparison."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cuser-guide%5Crule-path-syntax.md:64
msgid "Matching is **case-sensitive** after normalisation."
msgstr ""

